metadata.description: Auddia Inc. develops software technologies for audio media companies and consumers of audio media. The company's flagship product is Auddia App, a subscription based commercial free AM/FM software application. It also provides Vodacast, an interactive podcasting platform and application. The company was founded in 2012 and is headquartered in Boulder, Colorado.
